{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1d173490f4","title":"给李敏的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1021e6941a","index":0,"year":1949,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"1d173490f4"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"58ba06057d","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"1d173490f4","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李敏是毛泽东与贺子珍的女儿，小名叫“蚊饺”，又叫“娇娇”。毛泽东给女儿李敏写的这封信用的便是“娇娇”。"},{"id":"e1b993dfe4","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"1d173490f4","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"贺怡，江西省吉安市永新县人，毛泽东三弟毛泽罩之妻、贺子珍的胞妹。"}],"contents":[{"id":"808ff47c91","type":"title","text":"给李敏“的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"1d173490f4"},{"id":"58ba06057d","type":"paragraph","text":"娇娇：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"1d173490f4"},{"id":"e1b993dfe4","type":"paragraph","text":"看到了你的来信很高兴","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"1d173490f4"},{"id":"13bae7d7b2","type":"paragraph","text":"你是我亲生女儿，我是你的亲生父亲。你去苏联十多年一直未见过面，你一定长天了长高了吧？爸爸想念你，也很喜欢你，希望快快回到爸爸身边来。爸爸已请贺怡同志专程去东北接你了，爸爸欢迎你来。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"1d173490f4"},{"id":"5d077a63d5","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"1d173490f4"}],"page":{"id":"8c4532c31e","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"1d173490f4","start":114,"end":114}}}},"__N_SSG":true}